<promed@promedmail.org>
******
[2]
Date: Wed, 31 Aug 2005
From: ProMED-mail <promed@promedmail.org>
Source: Interfax.ru [edited]
<http://www.interfax.ru/e/B/politics/28.html?id_issue=11369656>

More than 30 residents of the villages of Volyny and Staroutkinsk in the
Sverdlovsk region have been hospitalized with suspected tularemia, the Federal
Consumer Rights and Welfare Service's Shalinsky district office told Interfax
on Wed, 31 Aug 2005.
2 other patients suspected of having contracted tularemia have been
hospitalized in Yekaterinburg, the hospital press service said.
--
ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>
